<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>About MentorKE</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; background-color: #f4f8fb; }
        .navbar { background-color: #0d47a1; padding: 15px; text-align: center; }
        .navbar a { color: white; margin: 0 15px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; }
        .header { background-color: #e3f2fd; padding: 30px; text-align: center; }
        .header h1 { color: #0d47a1; margin: 0; }
        .container { padding: 40px; max-width: 900px; margin: auto; }
        .card { background: white; padding: 25px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); margin-bottom: 20px; }
        h2 { color: #0d47a1; }
        p { color: #333; line-height: 1.6; }
        .footer { text-align: center; padding: 15px; background: #0d47a1; color: white; margin-top: 30px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class='navbar'>
        <a href='index'>Home</a>
        <a href='about'>About</a>
        <a href='register'>Register</a>
        <a href='login'>Login</a>
    </div>

    <div class='header'>
        <h1>About MentorKE</h1>
        <p>Empowering mentorship across Kenya</p>
    </div>

    <div class='container'>
        <div class='card'>
            <h2>Who We Are</h2>
            <p>MentorKE is a Kenyan-based mentorship management platform that connects experienced professionals with students and young individuals seeking guidance in their careers and personal growth.</p>
        </div>

        <div class='card'>
            <h2>Our Mission</h2>
            <p>Our mission is to make mentorship accessible, structured, and impactful by leveraging technology to bridge the gap between mentors and mentees.</p>
        </div>

        <div class='card'>
            <h2>What We Do</h2>
            <p>We provide a platform where mentors and mentees can connect, schedule sessions, track progress, and build meaningful professional relationships.</p>
        </div>

        <div class='card'>
            <h2>Why MentorKE?</h2>
            <p>Many young people in Kenya lack access to mentorship and career guidance. MentorKE helps solve this by creating a digital space for knowledge sharing, career growth, and opportunity.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class='footer'>
        <p>&copy; 2026 MentorKE | Built in Kenya</p>
    </div>
</body>
